-Da.

338
00:17:25,522 --> 00:17:26,901
Ponekad su naši izabranici

339
00:17:26,983 --> 00:17:29,737
zlobni narcisi, arogantni gadovi.

340
00:17:29,819 --> 00:17:30,945
...malo sporije.

341
