00:18:56,073 --> 00:18:58,075
Jebeš kolačiće sreće. Jebeš slatko-kiselo.

376
00:18:58,659 --> 00:19:02,371
Jebeš pekinšku patku. Jebeš svilu.
Jebeš jin. Jebeš jang.

377
00:19:02,913 --> 00:19:04,832
Erik kaže: „Jebeš Konfučija.”

378
00:19:06,166 --> 00:19:07,167
Hvala.

379
00:19:07,250 --> 00:19:08,294
